rge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/framework\">Curseforge</a></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Resourceful Lib</td>\n          <td>ThatGravyBoat</td>\n          <td>1.0.0+</td>\n          <td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/resourceful-lib\">Modrinth</a></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Sophisticated Core</td>\n          <td>P3pp3rF1y</td>\n          <td>1.1.0+</td>\n          <td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/sophisticated-core\">Curseforge</a></td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </details>\n    <details>\n      <summary>🔧 Create Mod & Extensions</summary>\n        <table>\n          <tr>\n            <th>Mod Name</th>\n            <th>Author</th>\n            <th>Versions Implemented</th>\n            <th>Web Link</th>\n          </tr>\n          <td>Create</td>\n            <td>simibubi</td>\n            <td>1.0.0+</td>\n            <td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create\">Modrinth</a></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Create Deco</td>\n            <td>talrey</td>\n            <td>1.6.0+</td>\n            <td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create-deco\">Modrinth</a></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Create Enchantment Industry</td>\n            <td>MarbleGateKeeper</td>\n            <td>1.0.0+</td>\n            <td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create-enchantment-industry\">Modrinth</a></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n             <td>Create Encased</td>\n             <td>iglee42</td>\n             <td>1.1.9.0+</td>\n             <td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create-encased\">Modrinth</a></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n             <td>Create: Bells & Whistles</td>\n             <td>lev</td>\n             <td>1.2.0+</td>\n             <td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/bellsandwhistles\">Modrinth</a></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n             <td>Create: Interiors</td>\n             <td>lev</td>\n             <td>1